isaServer.name: isaServer

revisions.description: The initial revision of this MIB module.

isaServer.contactinfo: Garth Williams 11135-23A Ave Edmonton, AB T6J4W5 Canada Tel: +1 780 434 4113 E-mail: garth.williams@wtcs.org
isaServer.description: The MIB module for SNMP Informant ISAServer performance counter entries.

h323Filter.name: h323Filter
h323Filter.description: The H.323 Firewall Filter object contains the counters for the number of H.323 calls handled by the H.323 Firewall Filter component of ISA Server

h323FilterActiveH323Calls.name: h323FilterActiveH323Calls
h323FilterActiveH323Calls.description: The number of H.323 calls that are currently active.

h323FilterTotalH323Calls.name: h323FilterTotalH323Calls
h323FilterTotalH323Calls.description: The total number of H.323 calls handled by the H.323 filter since the Firewall Service was started.

bandwidthControlTable.name: bandwidthControlTable
bandwidthControlTable.description: A table containing performance information for instances of 'ISA Server Bandwidth Control' objects.

bandwidthControlEntry.name: bandwidthControlEntry
bandwidthControlEntry.description: Performance information for one particular instance of 'ISA Server Bandwidth Control' object.

bwCtrlAssignedConnections.name: bwCtrlAssignedConnections
bwCtrlAssignedConnections.description: Counts the number of connections with an assigned bandwidth priority.

cache.name: cache
cache.description: The ISA Server Cache object type includes counters specific to the cache.

cacheActiveRefreshKBPerSec.name: cacheActiveRefreshKBPerSec
cacheActiveRefreshKBPerSec.description: The rate at which bytes of data are retrieved from the Internet to actively refresh popular URLs in the cache.

cacheActiveRefreshURLPerSec.name: cacheActiveRefreshURLPerSec
cacheActiveRefreshURLPerSec.description: The rate at which popular URLs in the cache are actively refreshed from the Internet.

cacheDiskRetrievedKBPerSec.name: cacheDiskRetrievedKBPerSec
cacheDiskRetrievedKBPerSec.description: The rate at which kilobytes of data are retrieved from the disk cache.

cacheDiskCacheAllocatedSpaceKB.name: cacheDiskCacheAllocatedSpaceKB
cacheDiskCacheAllocatedSpaceKB.description: The amount of space used for the disk cache (from the total disk space allocated for disk caching).

cacheDiskContentWritesPerSec.name: cacheDiskContentWritesPerSec
cacheDiskContentWritesPerSec.description: The amount of writes to the disk cache, per second.

cacheDiskFailPerSec.name: cacheDiskFailPerSec
cacheDiskFailPerSec.description: The number of I/O failures per second. An I/O failure occurs when ISA Server fails to read from or write to disk cache.

cacheDiskRetrieveURLPerSec.name: cacheDiskRetrieveURLPerSec
cacheDiskRetrieveURLPerSec.description: The rate at which URLs are retrieved from the disk cache.

cacheMaxURLsCached.name: cacheMaxURLsCached
cacheMaxURLsCached.description: The maximum number of URLs that have been stored in the cache.

cacheMemoryRetrievedKBPerSec.name: cacheMemoryRetrievedKBPerSec
cacheMemoryRetrievedKBPerSec.description: The rate at which kilobytes of data are retrieved from the memory cache.

cacheMemoryCacheAllocatedSpaceKB.name: cacheMemoryCacheAllocatedSpaceKB
cacheMemoryCacheAllocatedSpaceKB.description: The amount of space being used for the memory cache, from the memory allocated for memory caching.

cacheMemoryRetrieveURLPerSec.name: cacheMemoryRetrieveURLPerSec
cacheMemoryRetrieveURLPerSec.description: The rate at which URLs are retrieved from the memory cache.

cacheMemoryUsageRatioPercent.name: cacheMemoryUsageRatioPercent
cacheMemoryUsageRatioPercent.description: The amount of memory cache fetches, in proportion to total cache fetches.

cacheTotalActivelyRefreshedURLs.name: cacheTotalActivelyRefreshedURLs
cacheTotalActivelyRefreshedURLs.description: The cumulative number of popular URLs in the cache that have been actively refreshed from the Internet.

cacheTotalBytesActiveRefreshedKB.name: cacheTotalBytesActiveRefreshedKB
cacheTotalBytesActiveRefreshedKB.description: The total bytes retrieved from the Internet to actively refresh popular URLs in the cache.

cacheTotalDiskBytesRetrievedKB.name: cacheTotalDiskBytesRetrievedKB
cacheTotalDiskBytesRetrievedKB.description: The cumulative number of kilobytes retrieved from the disk cache.

cacheTotalDiskFailures.name: cacheTotalDiskFailures
cacheTotalDiskFailures.description: The number of times that ISA Server failed to read from or write to disk cache, due to an I/O failure, since the Web Proxy service started.

cacheTotalDiskURLsRetrieved.name: cacheTotalDiskURLsRetrieved
cacheTotalDiskURLsRetrieved.description: The cumulative number of URLs retrieved from the disk cache.

cacheTotalMemoryBytesRetrievedKB.name: cacheTotalMemoryBytesRetrievedKB
cacheTotalMemoryBytesRetrievedKB.description: The cumulative number of kilobytes retrieved from the memory cache.

cacheTotalMemoryURLsRetrieved.name: cacheTotalMemoryURLsRetrieved
cacheTotalMemoryURLsRetrieved.description: The cumulative number of URLs retrieved from the memory cache.

cacheTotalURLsCached.name: cacheTotalURLsCached
cacheTotalURLsCached.description: The cumulative number of URLs that have been stored in the cache.

cacheURLCommitPerSec.name: cacheURLCommitPerSec
cacheURLCommitPerSec.description: The rate at which URLs are committed to the cache.

cacheURLsInCache.name: cacheURLsInCache
cacheURLsInCache.description: The current number of URLs in the cache.

fsAcceptingTCPConnections.name: fsAcceptingTCPConnections
fsAcceptingTCPConnections.description: The number of connection objects waiting for a TCP connection from the Firewall client after a successful remote connection.

fsActiveSessions.name: fsActiveSessions
fsActiveSessions.description: The number of active Firewall service sessions.

fsActiveTCPConnections.name: fsActiveTCPConnections
fsActiveTCPConnections.description: The total number of active TCP connections currently passing data. Connections pending or not yet established are counted elsewhere.

fsActiveUDPConnections.name: fsActiveUDPConnections
fsActiveUDPConnections.description: The total number of active UDP connections.

fsAvailableWorkerThreads.name: fsAvailableWorkerThreads
fsAvailableWorkerThreads.description: The number of Firewall service worker threads that are available (waiting in completion port queue).

fsBackConnectingTCPConnections.name: fsBackConnectingTCPConnections
fsBackConnectingTCPConnections.description: The total number of TCP connections awaiting an inbound connect call to finish. These are connections from the Firewall service to a Firewall client after the Firewall service accepted a connection from the Internet on a listening socket.

fsBytesReadPerSec.name: fsBytesReadPerSec
fsBytesReadPerSec.description: Number of bytes read by the data-pump per second.

fsBytesWrittenPerSec.name: fsBytesWrittenPerSec
fsBytesWrittenPerSec.description: Number of bytes written by data-pump per second.

fsConnectingTCPConnections.name: fsConnectingTCPConnections
fsConnectingTCPConnections.description: The total number of TCP connections pending. This is the total number of connections that are waiting for a connect call to finish.

fsDNSCacheEntries.name: fsDNSCacheEntries
fsDNSCacheEntries.description: The current number of DNS domain name entries cached by the Firewall service.

fsDNSCacheFlushes.name: fsDNSCacheFlushes
fsDNSCacheFlushes.description: The total number of times that the DNS domain name cache has been flushed or cleared by the Web Proxy Server.

fsDNSCacheHits.name: fsDNSCacheHits
fsDNSCacheHits.description: The total number of times a DNS domain name was found within the DNS Cache.

fsDNSCacheHitsPercent.name: fsDNSCacheHitsPercent
fsDNSCacheHitsPercent.description: The percentage of DNS domain names serviced by the DNS cache, out of a total of all DNS entries that have been retrieved by the Firewall service.

fsDNSRetrievals.name: fsDNSRetrievals
fsDNSRetrievals.description: The total number of DNS domain names that have been retrieved by the Firewall service.

fsFailedDNSResolutions.name: fsFailedDNSResolutions
fsFailedDNSResolutions.description: Number of gethostbyname and gethostbyaddr API calls that have failed. These are calls used to resolve host DNS domain names and IP addresses for Firewall service connections.

fsKernelModeDataPumps.name: fsKernelModeDataPumps
fsKernelModeDataPumps.description: The number of kernel mode data pumps created by the Firewall service.

fsListeningTCPConnections.name: fsListeningTCPConnections
fsListeningTCPConnections.description: The number of connection objects waiting for TCP connections from remote Internet computers (after a successful listen).

fsNonConnectedUDPMappings.name: fsNonConnectedUDPMappings
fsNonConnectedUDPMappings.description: The number of mappings available for UDP connections.

fsPendingDNSResolutions.name: fsPendingDNSResolutions
fsPendingDNSResolutions.description: Number of gethostbyname and gethostbyaddr API calls pending resolution. These are calls used to resolve host DNS domain names and IP addresses for Firewall service connections.

fsSecureNATMappings.name: fsSecureNATMappings
fsSecureNATMappings.description: The number of mappings created by SecureNAT.

fsSuccessfulDNSResolutions.name: fsSuccessfulDNSResolutions
fsSuccessfulDNSResolutions.description: Number of gethostbyname and gethostbyaddr API calls successfully returned. These are calls used to resolve host DNS domain names and IP addresses for Firewall service connections.

fsTCPBytesXferPerSecByKernelMode.name: fsTCPBytesXferPerSecByKernelMode
fsTCPBytesXferPerSecByKernelMode.description: Number of TCP bytes transferred by the kernel mode data-pump per second.

fsUDPBytesXferPerSecByKernelMode.name: fsUDPBytesXferPerSecByKernelMode
fsUDPBytesXferPerSecByKernelMode.description: Number of UDP bytes transferred by the kernel mode data-pump per second.

fsWorkerThreads.name: fsWorkerThreads
fsWorkerThreads.description: The number of Firewall service worker threads that are currently alive.

fsAvailableUDPMappings.name: fsAvailableUDPMappings
fsAvailableUDPMappings.description: The number of mappings available for UDP connections.

fsDNSCacheLockFailures.name: fsDNSCacheLockFailures
fsDNSCacheLockFailures.description: The total number of times that the DNS domain names cache failed locking its internal data structure.

fsPendingTCPConnections.name: fsPendingTCPConnections
fsPendingTCPConnections.description: The total number of pending TCP connections. This is the total number of connections that are waiting for a connect call to finish.

fsTCPAwaitInConnectCallToFinish.name: fsTCPAwaitInConnectCallToFinish
fsTCPAwaitInConnectCallToFinish.description: The total number of TCP connections awaiting an inbound connect call to finish. These are connections from the Firewall Service to a Firewall client after the Firewall Service accepted a connection from the Internet on a listening socket.

firewallEngine.name: firewallEngine
firewallEngine.description: Microsoft Firewall Packet Engine performance counters.

feActiveConnections.name: feActiveConnections
feActiveConnections.description: The total number of active connections currently passing data.

feAllowedPackets.name: feAllowedPackets
feAllowedPackets.description: The total number of allowed packets.

feAllowedPacketsPerSec.name: feAllowedPacketsPerSec
feAllowedPacketsPerSec.description: The number of allowed packets per second.

feBytes.name: feBytes
feBytes.description: The total number of bytes passed through the firewall.

feBytesPerSec.name: feBytesPerSec
feBytesPerSec.description: The number of bytes passed through the firewall per second.

feConnectionsPerSec.name: feConnectionsPerSec
feConnectionsPerSec.description: The number of newly created connections per second.

feDroppedPackets.name: feDroppedPackets
feDroppedPackets.description: The total number of dropped packets.

feDroppedPacketsPerSec.name: feDroppedPacketsPerSec
feDroppedPacketsPerSec.description: The number of dropped packets per second.

fePackets.name: fePackets
fePackets.description: The total number of packets inspected by the firewall.

fePacketsPerSec.name: fePacketsPerSec
fePacketsPerSec.description: The number of packets inspected by the firewall per second.

feTCPEstablishedConnsPerSec.name: feTCPEstablishedConnsPerSec
feTCPEstablishedConnsPerSec.description: The number of newly TCP established connections per second. A TCP connection is counted as established after the 3-way SYN handshake was completed successfully.

feTCPEstablishedConns.name: feTCPEstablishedConns
feTCPEstablishedConns.description: The current number of established TCP connections. A TCP connection is counted as established after the 3-way SYN handshake was completed successfully.

packetsDroppedFilterDenial.name: packetsDroppedFilterDenial
packetsDroppedFilterDenial.description: The total number of packets dropped because dynamic packet filtering rejected the data.

packetsDroppedProtocolViolation.name: packetsDroppedProtocolViolation
packetsDroppedProtocolViolation.description: The total of the number of frames dropped because of a protocol irregularity.

totalDroppedPackets.name: totalDroppedPackets
totalDroppedPackets.description: The total number of dropped or filtered packets.

totalLoggingPacketsLost.name: totalLoggingPacketsLost
totalLoggingPacketsLost.description: The total of the number of packets dropped that could not be logged.

totalIncomingConn.name: totalIncomingConn
totalIncomingConn.description: The total number of connections made through the filtered interfaces.

webProxyService.name: webProxyService
webProxyService.description: The Web Proxy service object type includes counters specific to the ISA Server Web Proxy service.

wpsArrayBytesReceivedPerSec.name: wpsArrayBytesReceivedPerSec
wpsArrayBytesReceivedPerSec.description: The rate at which data bytes are received by the ISA Server from other servers within the same array in response to requests from the Web Proxy filter.

wpsArrayBytesSentPerSec.name: wpsArrayBytesSentPerSec
wpsArrayBytesSentPerSec.description: The rate at which data bytes are sent by the ISA Server to other servers within the same array.

wpsArrayBytesTotalPerSec.name: wpsArrayBytesTotalPerSec
wpsArrayBytesTotalPerSec.description: The sum of Array Bytes Sent/sec and Bytes Received/sec. This is the total rate for all bytes transferred between the ISA Server and other members of the same array.

wpsCacheHitRatioPercent.name: wpsCacheHitRatioPercent
wpsCacheHitRatioPercent.description: The percentage of Web Proxy client requests served using cached data, out of the total number of Web Proxy client requests to the ISA Server.

wpsCacheRunningHitRatioPercent.name: wpsCacheRunningHitRatioPercent
wpsCacheRunningHitRatioPercent.description: The percentage of Web Proxy client requests served using cached data out of the total number of Web Proxy client requests to the ISA Server, for the last 10,000 requests serviced.

wpsClientBytesReceivedPerSec.name: wpsClientBytesReceivedPerSec
wpsClientBytesReceivedPerSec.description: The rate at which data bytes are received by the Web Proxy filter from Web Proxy clients.

wpsClientBytesSentPerSec.name: wpsClientBytesSentPerSec
wpsClientBytesSentPerSec.description: The rate at which data bytes are sent by the Web Proxy filter to Web Proxy clients.

wpsClientBytesTotalPerSec.name: wpsClientBytesTotalPerSec
wpsClientBytesTotalPerSec.description: The sum of Client Bytes Sent/sec and Client Bytes Received/sec. This is the total rate for all bytes transferred between the Web Proxy filter and Web Proxy clients.

wpsConnectErrors.name: wpsConnectErrors
wpsConnectErrors.description: The total number of errors that occurred while connecting.

wpsConnErrsPerTotalErrsPercent.name: wpsConnErrsPerTotalErrsPercent
wpsConnErrsPerTotalErrsPercent.description: The percentage of errors that occurred while connecting as a ratio of the total number of failed requests during the time shown in the duration field.

wpsCurArrayFetchAvgMSPerRequest.name: wpsCurArrayFetchAvgMSPerRequest
wpsCurArrayFetchAvgMSPerRequest.description: The mean number of milliseconds required to service a Web Proxy client request that is fetched through another array member (not including requests serviced by the Secure Sockets Layer tunnel).

wpsCurAvgMSPerRequest.name: wpsCurAvgMSPerRequest
wpsCurAvgMSPerRequest.description: The mean number of milliseconds required to service a Web Proxy client request (not including requests serviced by the Secure Sockets Layer tunnel).

wpsCurCacheFetchAvgMSPerRequest.name: wpsCurCacheFetchAvgMSPerRequest
wpsCurCacheFetchAvgMSPerRequest.description: The mean number of milliseconds required to service a Web Proxy client request from cache (not including tunneled requests for HTTPS or SNEWS).

wpsCurDirectFetchAvgMSPerRequest.name: wpsCurDirectFetchAvgMSPerRequest
wpsCurDirectFetchAvgMSPerRequest.description: The mean number of milliseconds required to service a Web Proxy client request directly to the Web server or upstream proxy (not including tunneled requests for HTTPS or SNEWS).

wpsCurrentUsers.name: wpsCurrentUsers
wpsCurrentUsers.description: The number of users currently connected to the Web Proxy service.

wpsDNSCacheEntries.name: wpsDNSCacheEntries
wpsDNSCacheEntries.description: The current number of DNS domain name entries cached as a result of Web Proxy filter activity.

wpsDNSCacheFlushes.name: wpsDNSCacheFlushes
wpsDNSCacheFlushes.description: The total number of times that the DNS domain name cache was flushed by the Web Proxy filter.

wpsDNSCacheHits.name: wpsDNSCacheHits
wpsDNSCacheHits.description: The total number of times a DNS domain name was found in the DNS Cache by the Web Proxy filter.

wpsDNSCacheHitsPercent.name: wpsDNSCacheHitsPercent
wpsDNSCacheHitsPercent.description: The percentage of DNS domain names served from the DNS cache, out of a total of all DNS entries retrieved by the Web Proxy filter.

wpsDNSRetrievals.name: wpsDNSRetrievals
wpsDNSRetrievals.description: The total number of DNS domain names retrieved by the Web Proxy filter.

wpsFailRqstsPerTotalRqstsPercent.name: wpsFailRqstsPerTotalRqstsPercent
wpsFailRqstsPerTotalRqstsPercent.description: The percentage of failing requests out of the total number of requests during the time shown in the duration field.

wpsFailRqstsPerSec.name: wpsFailRqstsPerSec
wpsFailRqstsPerSec.description: The rate per second of requests that have failed because of some type of error.

wpsFailRqstsFromArrayMbr.name: wpsFailRqstsFromArrayMbr
wpsFailRqstsFromArrayMbr.description: The total number of requests coming from another array member.

wpsFailRqstsFromArrayMbrPerErrs.name: wpsFailRqstsFromArrayMbrPerErrs
wpsFailRqstsFromArrayMbrPerErrs.description: The percentage of requests coming from another array member out of the total number of failed requests.

wpsFailRqstsToArrayMbr.name: wpsFailRqstsToArrayMbr
wpsFailRqstsToArrayMbr.description: The total number of requests going to another array member.

wpsFailRqstsToArrayMbrPerErrs.name: wpsFailRqstsToArrayMbrPerErrs
wpsFailRqstsToArrayMbrPerErrs.description: The percentage of requests going to another array member out of the total number of failed requests.

wpsFailRqstsKAToArrayMbr.name: wpsFailRqstsKAToArrayMbr
wpsFailRqstsKAToArrayMbr.description: The total number of using an existing keep alive connection between the proxy and another array member.

wpsFailRqstsKAToArrayMbrPerErrs.name: wpsFailRqstsKAToArrayMbrPerErrs
wpsFailRqstsKAToArrayMbrPerErrs.description: The percentage of using an existing keep alive connection between the proxy and another array member out of the total number of failed requests.

wpsFailRqstsKAToClient.name: wpsFailRqstsKAToClient
wpsFailRqstsKAToClient.description: The total number of requests using an existing keep alive connection between the client and the proxy.

wpsFailRqstsKAToClientPerErrs.name: wpsFailRqstsKAToClientPerErrs
wpsFailRqstsKAToClientPerErrs.description: The percentage of requests using an existing keep alive connection between the client and the proxy out of the total number of failed requests.

wpsFailRqstsKAToServer.name: wpsFailRqstsKAToServer
wpsFailRqstsKAToServer.description: The total number of requests using an existing keep alive connection between the proxy and the web server.

wpsFailRqstsKAToServerPerErrs.name: wpsFailRqstsKAToServerPerErrs
wpsFailRqstsKAToServerPerErrs.description: The percentage of requests using an existing keep alive connection between the proxy and the web server out of the total number of failed requests.

wpsFtpRequests.name: wpsFtpRequests
wpsFtpRequests.description: The total number of FTP requests made to ISA Server, since the Firewall service was started.

wpsHTTPSSessions.name: wpsHTTPSSessions
wpsHTTPSSessions.description: The total number of HTTP-secured sessions serviced by the Secure Sockets Layer (SSL) tunnel. This includes only sessions allowed by rules configured to use SSL tunneling publishing mode.

wpsHttpRequests.name: wpsHttpRequests
wpsHttpRequests.description: The total number of HTTP requests made to ISA Server, since the Firewall service was started.

wpsIOErrorsToArrayMember.name: wpsIOErrorsToArrayMember
wpsIOErrorsToArrayMember.description: The total number of IO errors that occurred during communication with an array member.

wpsIOErrorsToArrayMemberPerErrs.name: wpsIOErrorsToArrayMemberPerErrs
wpsIOErrorsToArrayMemberPerErrs.description: The percentage of IO errors that occurred during communication with an array member out of the total number of failed requests during the time shown in the duration field.

wpsIOErrorsToClient.name: wpsIOErrorsToClient
wpsIOErrorsToClient.description: The total number of IO errors that occurred during communication with the client.

wpsIOErrorsToClientPerErrs.name: wpsIOErrorsToClientPerErrs
wpsIOErrorsToClientPerErrs.description: The percentage of IO errors that occurred during communication with the client out of the total number of failed requests during the time shown in the duration field.

wpsIOErrorsToServer.name: wpsIOErrorsToServer
wpsIOErrorsToServer.description: The total number of IO errors that occurred during communication with the server.

wpsIOErrorsToServerPerErrs.name: wpsIOErrorsToServerPerErrs
wpsIOErrorsToServerPerErrs.description: The percentage of IO errors that occurred during communication with the server out of the total number of failed requests during the time shown in the duration field.

wpsIncomingConnectionsPerSec.name: wpsIncomingConnectionsPerSec
wpsIncomingConnectionsPerSec.description: The rate per second of incoming connections.

wpsMaximumUsers.name: wpsMaximumUsers
wpsMaximumUsers.description: The maximum number of users that have connected to the ISA Server computer simultaneously, since the Firewall service was started.

wpsOutgoingConnectionsPerSec.name: wpsOutgoingConnectionsPerSec
wpsOutgoingConnectionsPerSec.description: The rate per second of outgoing connections.

wpsRequestsPerSec.name: wpsRequestsPerSec
wpsRequestsPerSec.description: The rate of requests that have been made to the Web Proxy filter.

wpsReverseBytesReceivedPerSec.name: wpsReverseBytesReceivedPerSec
wpsReverseBytesReceivedPerSec.description: The rate at which data bytes are received by the Web Proxy filter from published Web servers in response to incoming Web requests.

wpsReverseBytesSentPerSec.name: wpsReverseBytesSentPerSec
wpsReverseBytesSentPerSec.description: The rate at which data bytes are sent by the Web Proxy filter to published Web servers in response to incoming Web requests.

wpsReverseBytesTotalPerSec.name: wpsReverseBytesTotalPerSec
wpsReverseBytesTotalPerSec.description: The sum of Reverse Bytes Sent/sec and Reverse Bytes Received/sec. This is the total rate for all bytes transferred between the ISA Server and published Web servers in response to incoming Web requests.

wpsSNEWSSessions.name: wpsSNEWSSessions
wpsSNEWSSessions.description: The total number of SNEWS sessions serviced by the Secure Sockets Layer (SSL) tunnel. This includes only sessions allowed by rules configured to use SSL tunneling publishing mode.

wpsSSLClientBytesReceivedPerSec.name: wpsSSLClientBytesReceivedPerSec
wpsSSLClientBytesReceivedPerSec.description: The rate at which Secure Sockets Layer (SSL) data bytes are received by the Web Proxy filter from Web Proxy clients over a secure connection.

wpsSSLClientBytesSentPerSec.name: wpsSSLClientBytesSentPerSec
wpsSSLClientBytesSentPerSec.description: The rate at which Secure Sockets Layer (SSL) data bytes are sent by the Web Proxy filter to Web Proxy clients over a secure connection.

wpsSSLClientBytesTotalPerSec.name: wpsSSLClientBytesTotalPerSec
wpsSSLClientBytesTotalPerSec.description: The sum of SSL Client Bytes Sent/sec and Bytes Received/sec. This is the total rate for all bytes transferred between the Web Proxy filter and Web Proxy clients over a secure connection.

wpsSitesDenied.name: wpsSitesDenied
wpsSitesDenied.description: The total number of websites to which the Web Proxy filter denied access.

wpsSitesGranted.name: wpsSitesGranted
wpsSitesGranted.description: The total number of websites to which the Web Proxy filter allowed access.

wpsThreadPoolFailures.name: wpsThreadPoolFailures
wpsThreadPoolFailures.description: The number of requests rejected because the thread pool was overcommitted.

wpsThreadPoolSize.name: wpsThreadPoolSize
wpsThreadPoolSize.description: The number of threads in the thread pool.

wpsThreadPoolActiveSessions.name: wpsThreadPoolActiveSessions
wpsThreadPoolActiveSessions.description: The number of sessions actively serviced by thread pool threads.

wpsTotalArrayFetches.name: wpsTotalArrayFetches
wpsTotalArrayFetches.description: The total number of Web Proxy client requests that have been serviced by requesting the data from another ISA Server within the array.

wpsTotalCacheFetches.name: wpsTotalCacheFetches
wpsTotalCacheFetches.description: The total number of Web Proxy client requests served from the ISA Server cache.

wpsTotalFailingRequests.name: wpsTotalFailingRequests
wpsTotalFailingRequests.description: The total number of requests that failed to be processed due to errors. Errors can be the result of the Web Proxy filter failing to locate a requested server URL on the Internet or because the Web Proxy client was denied access to the requested URL.

wpsTotalPendingConnects.name: wpsTotalPendingConnects
wpsTotalPendingConnects.description: The total number of connection requests made, but not yet established.

wpsTotalRequests.name: wpsTotalRequests
wpsTotalRequests.description: The total number of requests made to ISA Server, since the Firewall service was started.

wpsTotalReverseFetches.name: wpsTotalReverseFetches
wpsTotalReverseFetches.description: The total number of incoming Web requests serviced by retrieving data from published Web servers.

wpsTotalSSLSessions.name: wpsTotalSSLSessions
wpsTotalSSLSessions.description: The total number of Secure Sockets Layer (SSL) sessions serviced by the SSL tunnel. This includes only sessions allowed by rules configured to use SSL tunneling publishing mode.

wpsTotalSuccessfulRequests.name: wpsTotalSuccessfulRequests
wpsTotalSuccessfulRequests.description: The total number of requests that were successfully processed by the Web Proxy filter.

wpsTotalUpstreamFetches.name: wpsTotalUpstreamFetches
wpsTotalUpstreamFetches.description: The total number of requests served by retrieving content from remote servers or from a chained upstream ISA Server computer.

wpsTotalUsers.name: wpsTotalUsers
wpsTotalUsers.description: The total number of users that have ever connected to the ISA Server computer, since the Firewall service was started.

wpsUnknownSSLSessions.name: wpsUnknownSSLSessions
wpsUnknownSSLSessions.description: The total number of unknown Secure Sockets Layer (SSL) sessions serviced by the SSL tunnel. This includes only sessions allowed by rules configured to use SSL tunneling publishing mode.

wpsUpstreamBytesReceivedPerSec.name: wpsUpstreamBytesReceivedPerSec
wpsUpstreamBytesReceivedPerSec.description: The rate at which data bytes are received by the Web Proxy filter from remote servers or from a chained upstream proxy.

wpsUpstreamBytesSentPerSec.name: wpsUpstreamBytesSentPerSec
wpsUpstreamBytesSentPerSec.description: The rate at which data bytes are sent by the Web Proxy filter to remote servers or to a chained upstream proxy.

wpsUpstreamBytesTotalPerSec.name: wpsUpstreamBytesTotalPerSec
wpsUpstreamBytesTotalPerSec.description: The total rate for all bytes transferred between ISA Server and remote servers or a chained upstream proxy.

wpsActiveWebSessions.name: wpsActiveWebSessions
wpsActiveWebSessions.description: The number of active Web sessions currently connected to ISA Server.

wpsAverageMillisecondsPerRequest.name: wpsAverageMillisecondsPerRequest
wpsAverageMillisecondsPerRequest.description: The mean number of milliseconds required to service a Web Proxy client request (not including tunneled requests for HTTPS or SNEWS).

wpsBytesRtnPtlCntRsps.name: wpsBytesRtnPtlCntRsps
wpsBytesRtnPtlCntRsps.description: The total number of bytes returned in responses to HTTP requests containing range headers.

wpsBytesRtnPtlCntRspsRqstdServer.name: wpsBytesRtnPtlCntRspsRqstdServer
wpsBytesRtnPtlCntRspsRqstdServer.description: The total number of bytes returned in responses to HTTP requests containing range headers requested from server.

wpsBytesRtnPtlCntRspsSvdCh.name: wpsBytesRtnPtlCntRspsSvdCh
wpsBytesRtnPtlCntRspsSvdCh.description: The total number of bytes returned in responses to HTTP requests containing range headers served from cache.

wpsBytesRtnPtlCntRspsSvdChHr.name: wpsBytesRtnPtlCntRspsSvdChHr
wpsBytesRtnPtlCntRspsSvdChHr.description: The total number of bytes returned in responses to HTTP requests containing range headers served from cache in the last hour.

wpsBytesRtnPtlCntRspsBITSEnChRule.name: wpsBytesRtnPtlCntRspsBITSEnChRule
wpsBytesRtnPtlCntRspsBITSEnChRule.description: The total number of bytes returned in responses to HTTP requests containing range headers for cache rules with BITS caching enabled.

wpsBytesRtnPtlCntRspsBITSEnChRuleHr.name: wpsBytesRtnPtlCntRspsBITSEnChRuleHr
wpsBytesRtnPtlCntRspsBITSEnChRuleHr.description: The total number of bytes returned in responses to HTTP requests containing range headers for cache rules with BITS caching enabled in the last hour.

wpsBytesRtnPtlCntRspsInLastHour.name: wpsBytesRtnPtlCntRspsInLastHour
